The Royal Enfield Scram 440 is a versatile, adventure-styled motorcycle featuring a new, more refined 443cc air/oil-cooled engine with 25.4 bhp and 34 Nm torque, paired with a 6-speed gearbox for better highway cruising. It offers dual-purpose tires, a comfortable upright riding position, switchable dual-channel ABS, and comes in spoke (Trail) or alloy (Force) wheel variants, blending classic looks with modern practical features for urban and light off-road fun. 
